「走出去请进来」，就实现了一个很好的成长之路，希望未来的女足更好。（央视新闻） "}, "image_area": {"url": ""}, "metrics_area": {"text": "76 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/587812387"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4IzNSb/Pay2uclEAMaCDkyOTA2NjM3INfvlKAGMAM4IUANcgk1ODc4MTIzODd4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "14_1678108609.9441845", "card_id": "Q_587687686", "card_label": {"type": "new", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-a4b0b52b561281109c51e4957cb20130_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-10ef6526c602e55a8c606e46aa0cc586_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 19}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "《狂飙》高启强为什么要给泰叔下跪，他就没有其他选择了吗？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "为什么高启强要给泰叔下跪，他就没有其他选择了吗？看完《狂飙》之后，相信很多人会有这样的疑惑，觉得高启强根本没必要找泰叔，徐江死了，头顶上的威胁也没了，安安稳稳过日子，他不香吗？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-d83fb6a24e3deb17314a0372ecf697d3_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "76 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/587687686"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4IzNSb/Pay2uclEAMaCDkyODc4OTE0IKSJkKAGMAA4H0AOcgk1ODc2ODc2ODZ4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "15_1678108609.944833", "card_id": "Q_586267096", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 39}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "幼儿园中班的宝宝学习跆拳道好一些，还是学习拳击好一些？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picb.zhimg.com/50/v2-3cfe0f5e4899f5c652ad67dd3af88759_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "74 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/586267096"}}, "attached_info": "